messages.message: LuminAI is planning to use the chatbot API as they migrate their use cases from converse community to their commercial account. I know itâ€™s preview for 24.30. Can we give them early access to this? If so, how would we do it? Cc @avi @Balaram

@hannah yes, we should be good to give early access to LuminAI.

We have put up (under review) a quick start guide (https://docs.google.com/document/d/16eMTeOxSTFxnNeiK4wUJZBrzvyzHNfOTRgDLodNxPtY/edit) to enable the developers to use the API. We should be good to share the APIs around Thursday (8th August)
